  "prompt": "What are cars of tata?",
  "response": "Tata Motors, a part of the Tata Group, is an Indian automobile manufacturer that produces a wide range of vehicles. As of my last update in October 2023, here are some of the notable car models offered by Tata:\n\n### Passenger Cars\n1. **Tata Nano** - A compact city car that was famous for being one of the most affordable cars in the world.\n2. **Tata Tiago** - A popular hatchback known for its stylish design and good performance.\n3. **Tata Tigor** - A compact sedan that shares its platform with the Tiago, offering additional boot space.\n4. **Tata Altroz** - A premium hatchback that comes with advanced safety features and a spacious interior.\n5. **Tata Harrier** - A mid-size SUV that features a robust design and is available with various high-tech features.\n6. **Tata Safari** - A larger SUV based on the Harrier platform, known for its spaciousness and comfort.\n7. **Tata Nexon** - A subcompact SUV that has gained popularity for its design, features, and safety ratings.\n8. **Tata Punch** - A micro SUV that combines compact dimensions with practicality and modern styling.\n9. **Tata Curvv** - An upcoming SUV that aims to blend modern aesthetics with advanced technology.\n\n### Electric Vehicles\n1. **Tata Nexon EV** - An electric version of the Nexon, offering zero emissions and good range.\n2. **Tata Tigor EV** - The electric variant of the Tigor sedan.\n3. **Tata Tiago EV** - An electric version of the Tiago hatchback aimed at urban drivers.\n4. **Tata Avinya** - An upcoming electric vehicle that focuses on futuristic design and technology.\n\n### Commercial Vehicles\nTata Motors also produces a range of commercial vehicles including trucks, buses, vans, and other utility vehicles under various names and categories.\n\nTata Motors continues to innovate and expand its product lineup, so it's advisable to check their official website or local dealerships for the latest information on models and features.",
